response.overview: WWE Clash in Paris is an upcoming professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) and live-streaming event produced by the American company WWE. It will be the third Clash event, truncated from the previous "Clash at the Castle" name used in 2022 and 2024. The event will take place on Sunday, August 31, 2025, at the Paris La Défense Arena in La Défense, Nanterre, France, marking WWE's second PPV and livestreaming event held in France after Backlash France in May 2024, and the first in the Paris metropolitan area. It will be held for wrestlers from the promotion's Raw and SmackDown brand divisions.
response.title: WWE Clash in Paris 2025
